    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't want to \"keep moving forward\" though. what am i moving forward to? just more silence and more empty rooms? it feels like i'm just dragging this body around for no reason. honestly, it feels less like living and more like being punished. it's exhausting to just exist when the part of me that actually mattered is gone.",
